title: Week 5 picks & Vikings vs. Packers recap
itunes:title: Week 5 picks & Vikings vs. Packers recap
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- preview every game on the Week 5 NFL schedule and recap the Packers 42-10 win over the Vikings.
